Dear Sam and Colby,

One day I would like to meet you and the squad. You all truly mean a lot to me. I just had a very very emotional malt down because someone scammed me in my game :( Watching your Sam and Colby vids truly calms me down and makes my day. If I had the choice to kill myself or the whole squad, I would choose myself because I would never want and harm for you all
You guys reading this right now might just think, “oh it’s another fan” but no. I actually spend time out of my day. And all I do is watch you guys because that’s the only thing I can do. You help me threw so much. I’m LITTERALLY ur biggest fan. I would die to meet you. I love you and the squad more then I love myself. Even my friends think I’m a little weird by loving you guys so much.
You guys are my world. Now this might seem a little awkward that I’m saying all this but everything I wrote down today was true. I would beat the haters up if I saw one of them, I really hope you see this. Which you probs won’t but whatevs...I’m going to ask my father for some tickets to ur next tour when u have one.
No matter if I’m so so so so so so mad at you and the squad for a reason I would never stop loving you. I really hope you understand this message..and read it. I would absolutely love if I got to spend a day with you and the squad. And I would be still grateful if I at least got to hug you and meet you for like 1min..I know this is awkward but I never knew that one day I would go into a whole new world full of happiness because of you guys..love you and hopefully you read this because I spent like 1hour on this.❤️😭❤️😭❤️😭

His dream for getting far with his career helps me so much and I honestly don’t know what I would do if he hadn’t made me realize the people around me who’ll help me get there, achieve something so amazing. He makes me wanna give life and meaning and happiness to others and that’s what I’ll do. If being inspired by Sam Golbach means I’ll succeed in something passionate then why not try.
